cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.NE 

The paper deals with image recognition using deep learning techniques, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of convolutional neural networks (CNNs) also suggests that the paper could be categorized under artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also deals with information retrieval (cs.IR) as it involves identifying and categorizing images based on their content. Finally, the use of neural networks for classification suggests that the paper could also be categorized under neural networks (cs.NE).
